 Qitmeer Cross-chain Atomic-Swapping Through this tutorial, we demonstrate the QITMEER/BTC atomic-swapp by using qitmeer-cli and qx tool under the qitmeer TestNet.
Introduction What&rsquo;s Atomic-swapping &hellip;
Prerequisites  golang qitmeer-cli qx tool  Step By Step QIMEER/BTC Atomicswap Demo Prepare Private Key &amp; Address Create Secret Key &amp; Secret Key Hash Create Qitmeer HTLC (Hash Time-Lock Contract) Broadcasting transaction Verify Create BTC HTLC Broadcasting transaction Unlock BTC/Qitmeer HTLC User get BTC/Qitmeer
